#: ../../ai.rst:33
msgid "Choosing an LLM for code explanations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:35
msgid "In the RemixAI Assistant, there is a choice of LLMs for use in **code explanations** and in the AI Assistant."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:38
msgid "The default LLM is **MistralAI**. Click the MistralAI button and a modal will pop up where you can select **Anthropic**, **OpenAI**, or **MistralAI**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:41
msgid "RemixAI LLM dropdown menu"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:44
msgid "The RemixAI Assistant responds in the language in which it is asked and can answer questions about Solidity, JavaScript/TypeScript, Vyper, and other programming languages."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:49
msgid "You can click the **Explain Contract** button at the bottom of the Editor when a ``.sol`` file is active."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:54
msgid "Using a local LLM for privacy"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:56
msgid "When using an LLM, unless the model is running locally, your inputs may be used by the provider for training or retention. This means the information you submit could be stored or reused."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:60
msgid "If you want to use AI tools while keeping your information private, you can use a **local LLM**."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:63
msgid "Remix supports **Ollama**, a local AI model runner that allows you to download and run large language models (LLMs) directly on your own machine."
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:66
msgid "The Ollama LLMs supported by Remix include:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:68
msgid "``codestral:latest``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:69
msgid "``quen3-coder:latest``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:70
msgid "``gpt-oss:latest``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:71
msgid "``deepseek-coder-v2:latest`` (recommended for code completion)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:73
msgid "In addition to privacy, Remix’s Ollama integration provides:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:75
msgid "**No API rate throttling** – no usage fees or rate limits"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:76
msgid "**Offline capability** – works without an internet connection"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:77
msgid "**Fill-in-the-Middle (FIM) support** – advanced code completion features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../ai.rst:80
msgid "The Ollama integration does not support agentic workflows available in the online RemixAI service, such as Remix MCP or generating and editing Workspaces. Its capabilities are limited to code completion and conversational interactions."
msgstr ""

